Package lib

Class RequestVoteArgs

  • java.lang.Object
    • lib.RequestVoteArgs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class RequestVoteArgs
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is a wrapper for packing all the arguments that you might use in the RequestVote call, and should be serializable to fill in the payload of Message to be sent. Invoked by candidates to garher votes(§5.2)
